Package: VendiScore
Type: Package
Title: A metric for evaluating diversity in ML and the natural sciences 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Friedman", "Dan", email="dfriedman@princeton.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Pasarkar", "Amey", email = "amey.pasarkar@princeton.edu", role = "ctb"),
    person("Dieng", "Adji Bousso", email = "adji@princeton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Princeton Vertaix Lab", role = c("cph")))
Description: Implementation of the Vendi Scores, a family of diversity metrics,
    that can be employed across the sciences. The Vendi Scores only require a user-defined
    pair-wise similarity metric to be employed on any dataset.
URL: https://github.com/vertaix/Vendi-Score-R
